DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC WORKS TERMS UNDER THREE MONTHS EXCLUSION APPROVAL ORDER, 1993 - which exempts short-term jobs at the Department of Public Works from the application of the Public Service Employment Act, and 2. DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC WORKS TERMS UNDER THREE MONTHS REGULATIONS, 1993 - which establish the terms of employment for short-term positions. .
